snippet: Foreign Minister Héctor Timerman warns the United States, Israel and others to stay out of the case of the mysterious death of the prosecutor Alberto Nisman.
abstract: Argentinian Foreign Min Hector Timerman sends letter to Sec of State John Kerry, warning United States and other countries to stay out of nation's domestic issues, such as case of mysterious death of prosecutor Alberto Nisman.
lead_paragraph: Foreign Minister Héctor Timerman warns the United States, Israel and others to stay out of the case of the mysterious death of the prosecutor Alberto Nisman.

headline.main: Fallout Over Argentine Prosecutor’s Death Draws International Tensions
